<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">est 8:0</span></span>

Overview

[Est 8:1](../../../bib/kjv/est008.htm#001.md), Mordecai is advanced; [Est
8:3](../../../bib/kjv/est008.htm#003.md), Esther makes suit to reverse
Haman's letters; [Est 8:7](../../../bib/kjv/est008.htm#007.md), Ahasuerus
grants to the Jews to defend themselves; [Est
8:15](../../../bib/kjv/est008.htm#015.md), Mordecai's honour, and the Jews'
joy.

